install xaamp, mysql

create b2Connect table

open terminal 

navigate to app.module
enable synchronize:true

$ npm install

$ npm start


make a post request to http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
headers should have Content-Type : 'application/json'
sample data
{
    username:test
    password:test
}

